div.p: This module simply help to write history of changes after User editing product inside inventory. It will be saved inside odoo chatter or odoo logs upon saving.

ol.li: Download this module and put it inside your default Odoo Addons file.
From Odoo interface, enter the debug mode > Apps menu > update apps
In the search bar, delete everything and type in module name (Edit History of Inventory)
Refresh your browser, now the module will work in product template after editing and saving
